<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />辛苦你昨天<delay20 />担任圣诞老人的助手啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞礼物中满溢着<delay20 />
圣诞老人和你对我的关爱<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它就是我的宝物了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天你送来的<delay20 />
来自圣诞老人的礼物<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我高兴得反复看了好几遍呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天谢谢你了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你送的圣诞礼物，<delay20 />
真是太叫我开心了<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的平安夜将因为你<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而成为我最棒的回忆。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞快乐！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你昨天<delay20 />送来礼物。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和你交换了礼物这件事，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我最美好的回忆。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />谢谢你，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只因为是平安夜，<delay20 />
昨天就已经是个特别的日子了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是你和圣诞老人<delay20 />
送来的礼物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让它变成了尤为特别的日子。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一个快乐的圣诞节<delay20 />
就是这样的吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不仅收到了来自圣诞老人的礼物，<delay20 />
还得到了你馈赠的礼物，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的心里被爱填得满满当当了。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能够在圣诞节结束之前<delay frames="30" />
找到机会对你这么说，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太令我感到愉快了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞快乐！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我指的是这句祝福哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圣诞礼物这件物品<delay20 />
通常会在回忆中占有一席之地，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，我并不执着于这样的实物。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在名为圣诞节的这一特别之日，<delay20 />
能与<tag a="110" b="4" />你相见<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就已经为我带来十足的幸福感了。</message>
</msbt>